  temperamentText: Dell shows up early, tunes twice, and keeps the floor under everybody
    else. He will not steal the night, but he will keep it from falling apart.
  worksWellWithText: He works best with singers and soloists who respect the rhythm
    section.
  watchOutForText: He has little patience for divas, showboats, or players who treat
    timing like a suggestion.
